riscVivid v1.2
==============
- fork of openDLX v1.0-6
- replaced MIPS/DLX by RISC-V


riscVivid v1.3
==============
- minor improvements
- font size can now be increased/decreased via icons or Ctrl + Mousewheel
- check boxes to toggle between hex and decimal display of values

riscVivid v1.4
==============
- automatic formatting
- number of branch delay slots is switchable from 2 to 3
- forwarding and ignoring branch delay slots can be deactivated
- find/replace dialog for the editor 
- optional warning if unreserved memory is accessed
- optional warning if an uninitialized register is read
- syscalls are handled by flushing the pipeline and restarting the subsequent instruction
- breakpoint implementation